# 📝 Sai's Todo List

A simple and stylish **React Todo App** built with functional components and hooks.  
This project demonstrates state management using React's `useState`, props drilling, and basic CRUD functionality.

---

## ✨ Features

- ➕ Add new todos
- ✅ Mark todos as completed (checkbox)
- ❌ Delete todos
- 🎨 Clean, responsive UI with modern CSS styling
- ⚡ Built with **Vite + React**

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- [React](https://react.dev/) – Frontend library
- [Vite](https://vitejs.dev/) – Fast build tool
- [CSS3](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS) – Styling

